AQBAJ&amp;pg=PA26" class="external text external" id="mwBEA"><i id="mwBEE">Chaucer: A European Life</i></a>. Princeton University Press. p.<span id="mwBEI">&nbsp;</span>26. <a href="ISBN_(identifier)" title="ISBN (identifier)" class="mw-redirect" id="mwBEM">ISBN</a><span id="mwBEQ">&nbsp;</span><bdi id="mwBEY">978-0-691-16009-2</bdi>.</cite></span></li><li id="cite_note-10"><a href="Geoffrey_Chaucer#cite_ref-10" id="mwBEg"><span class="mw-linkback-text" id="mwBEk">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-10" class="mw-reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFBriggs2019" class="citation journal cs1">Briggs, Keith (June 2019). "The Malins in Chaucer's Ipswich Ancestry". <i id="mwBEs"><a href="Notes_and_Queries" title="Notes and Queries" id="mwBEw">Notes and Queries</a></i>. <b id="mwBE0">66</b> (2): 201–202. <a href="Doi_(identifier)" title="Doi (identifier)" class="mw-redirect" id="mwBE4">doi</a>:<a href="https://doi.org/10.1093%2Fnotesj%2Fgjz004" class="external text external" id="mwBE8">10.1093/notesj/gjz004</a>.</cite></span></li><li id="cite_note-11"><a href="Geoffrey_Chaucer#cite_ref-11" id="mwBFE"><span class="mw-linkback-text" id="mwBFI">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-11" class="mw-reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFHanksCoatesMcClure2016" class="citation book cs1"><a href="Patrick_Hanks" title="Patrick Hanks" id="mwBFQ">Hanks, Patrick</a>; <a href="Richard_Coates" title="Richard Coates" id="mwBFU">Coates, Richard</a>; McClure, Peter, eds. (2016). "Chaucer". <a href="https://www.oxfordreference.com/view/10.1093/acref/9780199677764.001.0001/acref-9780199677764-e-07364" class="external text external" id="mwBFY"><i id="mwBFc">The Oxford Dictionary of Family Names in Britain and Ireland</i></a>. Oxford UP. <a href="ISBN_(identifier)" title="ISBN (identifier)" class="mw-redirect" id="mwBFg">ISBN</a><span id="mwBFk">&nbsp;</span><bdi id="mwBFs">978-0-19-967776-4</bdi>.</cite></span></li><li id="cite_note-12"><a href="Geoffrey_Chaucer#cite_ref-1